<div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Invoice Generator</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Create professional invoices with line items, tax calculation, and downloadable formatted text output.</p>

    <div class="mb-8"><%= render "shared/ad_slot", slot: "leaderboard" %></div>

    <div data-controller="invoice-pdf-generator-calculator ad-engagement" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Invoice # *</label>
            <input type="text" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="invoiceNumber" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm font-mono" placeholder="INV-001">
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Date *</label>
            <input type="date" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="date" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Due Date *</label>
            <input type="date" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="dueDate" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">From (Name) *</label>
            <input type="text" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="fromName" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm" placeholder="Your Company Name">
            <input type="text" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="fromAddress" class="w-full mt-2 rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm" placeholder="Address (optional)">
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">To (Name) *</label>
            <input type="text" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="toName" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm" placeholder="Client Name">
            <input type="text" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="toAddress" class="w-full mt-2 rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm" placeholder="Address (optional)">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
          <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">Line Items</label>
          <div data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="lineItems" class="space-y-2">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-2 items-end" data-line-item>
              <div class="col-span-6">
                <label class="block text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Description</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Service or product" data-field="description" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-2">
                <label class="block text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Qty</label>
                <input type="number" placeholder="1" value="1" min="0.01" step="1" data-field="quantity" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-3">
                <label class="block text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Unit Price</label>
                <input type="number" placeholder="0.00" min="0" step="0.01" data-field="unit_price" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-1"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button data-action="click->invoice-pdf-generator-calculator#addItem" class="mt-3 text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">+ Add Item</button>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Tax Rate (%)</label>
            <input type="number" data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="taxRate" value="0" min="0" max="100" step="0.1" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Currency</label>
            <select data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="currency" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm">
              <option value="USD">USD ($)</option>
              <option value="EUR">EUR</option>
              <option value="GBP">GBP</option>
              <option value="JPY">JPY</option>
              <option value="CAD">CAD</option>
              <option value="AUD">AUD</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl">
          <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Notes <span class="text-gray-400 font-normal">(optional)</span></label>
          <textarea data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="notes" rows="2" class="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700 text-sm" placeholder="Payment terms, bank details, etc."></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <button data-action="click->invoice-pdf-generator-calculator#generate" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-indigo-700 text-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-200">Generate Invoice</button>
          <button data-action="click->invoice-pdf-generator-calculator#copy" class="px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200">Copy</button>
          <button data-action="click->invoice-pdf-generator-calculator#download" class="px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200">Download .txt</button>
        </div>

        <div data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="error" class="hidden p-3 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-xl text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 text-sm"></div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Invoice Preview</h2>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm font-semibold">
              <span>Subtotal: <span data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="resultSubtotal">$0.00</span></span>
              <span>Tax: <span data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="resultTax">$0.00</span></span>
              <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Total: <span data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="resultTotal">$0.00</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <textarea data-invoice-pdf-generator-calculator-target="output" readonly rows="20" class="w-full font-mono text-xs bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:outline-none resize-y" placeholder="Click 'Generate Invoice' to create your invoice..."></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render "shared/calculator_rating", slug: "invoice-pdf-generator" %>
    <div class="mb-8"><%= render "shared/ad_slot", slot: "in_results" %></div>

    <article class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2>How to Create an Invoice</h2>
      <p>
        An invoice is a document sent by a seller to a buyer requesting payment for goods or services. This generator creates professionally formatted invoices with all the essential elements: unique invoice number, dates, sender and recipient information, itemized line items with quantities and prices, tax calculation, and a total amount due. Fill in the form above and click Generate to create your invoice.
      </p>
      <p>
        Each line item includes a description, quantity, and unit price. The calculator automatically computes line totals, subtotal, tax, and grand total. You can add as many line items as needed using the Add Item button. The tax rate is applied to the subtotal. Set it to zero for tax-exempt invoices.
      </p>

      <div class="my-6"><%= render "shared/ad_slot", slot: "in_content" %></div>

      <h2>Invoice Best Practices</h2>
      <p>
        Use sequential invoice numbers for easy tracking and accounting. Set clear payment terms in the notes section, such as "Net 30" (payment due within 30 days) or "Due upon receipt." Include your preferred payment methods and bank details. Send invoices promptly after delivering goods or services to maintain cash flow.
      </p>

      <h3>Tax Considerations</h3>
      <p>
        Tax rates vary by jurisdiction. In the US, sales tax ranges from 0% to over 10% depending on the state and locality. The EU uses VAT rates ranging from 17% to 27%. Some services and products may be tax-exempt. Consult your accountant or local tax authority to determine the correct rate for your invoices. Always include the tax amount as a separate line for transparency.
      </p>

      <h3>Record Keeping</h3>
      <p>
        Keep copies of all invoices for at least seven years for tax purposes. Organize them by invoice number or date for easy retrieval. Track payment status to identify overdue invoices. Send polite reminders for payments past their due date. Consider using accounting software for invoicing at scale.
      </p>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3>How do I create an invoice?</h3>
      <p>Enter invoice number, dates, sender/recipient details, add line items, set tax rate, and click Generate Invoice.</p>

      <h3>What should an invoice include?</h3>
      <p>Invoice number, dates, sender and recipient info, itemized line items, subtotal, tax, total, and payment terms.</p>

      <h3>How does tax calculation work?</h3>
      <p>The tax rate percentage is applied to the subtotal. A $1,000 subtotal with 10% tax adds $100 for a $1,100 total.</p>

      <h3>What currencies are supported?</h3>
      <p>USD, EUR, GBP, JPY, CAD, and AUD with their respective symbols. No currency conversion is performed.</p>

      <h3>Can I download the invoice?</h3>
      <p>Yes, click Download to save as a text file. Print to PDF using your browser's print function for PDF format.</p>

      <%= render "shared/print_button" %>
      <%= render "shared/calculation_email_capture" %>
    </article>

